            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "That is always the case for level=ERROR: https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/7d99104058fd2653903830c2b39b42d80092e646/runtime/lua/vim/_core/editor.lua#L688\n\n\nIt is an \"error\" in the `:echoerr` sense, not in the `error()` sense.\n",
